#include<stdio.h>
typedef struct
{
int x1,x2,x3,x4,y1,y2,y3,y4;
}rec;
int main()
{
rec r1,r2,r3;
int t;
scanf("%d",&t);
while(t--)
{
scanf("%d%d%d%d",&r1.x1,&r1.y1,&r1.x2,&r1.y2);
scanf("%d%d%d%d",&r2.x1,&r2.y1,&r2.x2,&r2.y2);
if(r2.x1<=r1.x2&&r2.y1<=r1.y2)
{
r3.x3=r2.x1;
r3.y3=r2.y2;
r3.x4=r1.x2;
r3.y4=r1.y1;
printf("%d %d %d %d\n",r3.x3,r3.y4,r3.x4,r3.y3);
}
else printf("No Overlap\n");
}
}
